Meet iLyn

An open source virtual assistant made for you

About iLyn

What's iLyn?

iLyn is the space where you meet with Lynessa!

Lynessa is an open source virtual assistant who uses AI to help you become a better version of yourself

About me

Who am I?

I'm William! Nice to meet you!

I am a software developer who has created Lynessa, an open-source virtual assistant that utilizes AI. This is my final project for my higher professional education, and I am excited to contribute my skills to the open source community. With Lynessa, I hope to provide a useful tool to simplify people's daily tasks and improve their productivity.

Features

What Lynessa can do for you

Task management

Lynessa can sort your tasks!

Conversational

Lynessa loves to talk to people!!!

Support

Lynessa can suggest activities based on your use of iLyn!

Ask her anything you want!

Lynessa uses the internet to ask your questions!

What are you waiting for?

Don't miss out on everything iLyn has to offer, sign up now and take advantage of our amazing features!

Start using now!
